@@$TJvScrollEvStringGrid
<TITLE TJvScrollEvStringGrid overview>
<GROUP JVCL.Miscel>
  TJvScrollEvStringGrid is a string grid that adds events to TStringGrid, that allow you to respond
  when the user scrolls the scroll bars of the grid.
  
  * You can use the OnBeforeHScroll and OnBeforeVScroll to prevent the user from scrolling the grid,
    by setting allowScroll to False.
  * Use OnAfterHScroll and OnAfterVScroll to respond when the user stops scrolling the scroll bars of
    the grid.
