@@TJvScrollEvStringGrid
<GROUP TJvScrollEvStringGrid>
Summary
  String grid that can respond to scroll events.
Description
  Use TJvScrollEvStringGrid if you want a string grid that can respond when the user scrolls the
  scroll bars of the string grid.
  
  Check scrollcode in the scroll events to take specific actions depending on the type of scroll 
  request.
  
  Prevent users from scrolling the grid by settings allowScroll to False in the OnBeforeHScroll or 
  OnBeforeVScroll event.
